snippet.title: Manta Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Promotional trailer for Manta.  Pilot an experimental biological ship which is both air superiority fighter and attack submarine.  Command a fleet of futuristic warships to aid you.  Build undersea missile bases.  Lead your fleet to victory!
